T1  - Time and No Lotteries: An Axiomatization of Maxmin Expected Utility
AU  - Kochov, Asen
Y1  - 2015/01/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA10886
T2  - Econometrica
